text: Baranovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Baranovsky Selsoviet, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 676 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 6 km NNW from Narimanov. == References == Category:Rural localities in Narimanovsky District
title: Baranovka, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
